    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts easily and runs smoothly, and the transmission provides reliable shifting through all gears. While the exterior paint retains a nice luster, you may find a few minor surface scratches or small stone chips consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major electronics and climate control systems functioning as they should. This is a dependable vehicle that is ready for daily driving and offers a great balance of performance and value.",
