    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is immaculate, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all systems performing at peak levels and a comprehensive service history that confirms its meticulous upkeep. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in showroom state, offering the highest level of quality and reliability for the next owner.",
