    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go and looks great doing it! I've taken good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
