      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response and linear power to an 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, while the Variable M Differential Lock ensures maximum traction out of corners. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and solid subframe mounts. This is a mechanically sound example of BMW M's high-revving zenith, ready for the street or technical circuit.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
