    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Porsche Macan in a striking Deep Sea Blue. This vehicle has been a joy to own, offering a perfect blend of performance and utility. The interior features premium black leather that remains supple and free of tears, though the driver's side bolster shows very light entry wear. Mechanically, she is sound; I have kept up with every scheduled service interval, and the engine pulls as smoothly as the day I bought it. The tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced last fall. You will notice a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger rim, consistent with careful daily use. This is a reliable, high-performance SUV that looks fantastic and drives even better. Includes two keys and a full folder of service receipts.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
